  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>(!!!Epilepsy Warning, This Game contains scenes with flashing lights!!!)</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WELCOME TO ULTRA X-TREME HUNTING SIMULATOR 2001:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ULTRA X-TREME HUNTING SIMULATOR 2001</strong> will bring the classic arcade experience from 1995 to your bedroom with this fast paced, <strong>addictive</strong> arcade <strong>shooter</strong>! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hunt and Kill as many deer as you can!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492250/extras/0f54d9eb1105628ad0c5808de169dc27.avif?t=1758148053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492250/extras_big/0f54d9eb1105628ad0c5808de169dc27.avif?t=1758148053 width=800 height=502 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore  Sequota National Forest!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492250/extras/285bea7020a1dd77c5be0a25f7fea92f.avif?t=1758148053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492250/extras_big/285bea7020a1dd77c5be0a25f7fea92f.avif?t=1758148053 width=800 height=502 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>7 Level Locations! 42 Hunting Spots! 3 Extra Challenge Levels(coming soon)!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The all new control and aim mechanics will make this a must pick up and play <u>arcade shooter experience</u>. Travel around and take down wild game in the many levels and <strong>bonus challenges</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone and compete for the highest score! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The perfect game</strong> for <strong>Hot Blooded Hunters</strong>, with <u>easy to pick up controls</u> that still pack a challenge for experienced players!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>(!!!Epilepsy Warning, This Game contains scenes with flashing lights!!!)</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WELCOME TO ULTRA X-TREME HUNTING SIMULATOR 2001:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ULTRA X-TREME HUNTING SIMULATOR 2001</strong> will bring the classic arcade experience from 1995 to your bedroom with this fast paced, <strong>addictive</strong> arcade <strong>shooter</strong>! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hunt and Kill as many deer as you can!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492250/extras/0f54d9eb1105628ad0c5808de169dc27.avif?t=1758148053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492250/extras_big/0f54d9eb1105628ad0c5808de169dc27.avif?t=1758148053 width=800 height=502 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore  Sequota National Forest!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492250/extras/285bea7020a1dd77c5be0a25f7fea92f.avif?t=1758148053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492250/extras_big/285bea7020a1dd77c5be0a25f7fea92f.avif?t=1758148053 width=800 height=502 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>7 Level Locations! 42 Hunting Spots! 3 Extra Challenge Levels(coming soon)!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The all new control and aim mechanics will make this a must pick up and play <u>arcade shooter experience</u>. Travel around and take down wild game in the many levels and <strong>bonus challenges</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone and compete for the highest score! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The perfect game</strong> for <strong>Hot Blooded Hunters</strong>, with <u>easy to pick up controls</u> that still pack a challenge for experienced players!</p>",
